@NODE Do_czego "General informations"

PCBDesigner is a program for comfortable and quick designing of
@{"printed circuit borads" LINK GLOSSARY}. It is useful for electronic engineers and
hobbyists. Here is a short list of features:

- fully vectorized scalable graphics,
- uses @{"MUI"  LINK "MUI"} for graphics user interface,
- system friendly - should work under CyberGfx (not tested yet),
- localization (Polish catalog and .cd .ct files included),
- acceptable speed even on a stock A1200.

There are of course only already implemented features.  In future versions a
lot of new possibilities will be added.  PCBDesigner 0.34 has  limited  edit
modes.  @{"Track" LINK GLOSSARY} width can vary from 1 to 9999 @{"mils" LINK GLOSSARY}. @{"Pads" LINK "GLOSSARY"} are fixed for now,
they have 75 @{"mils" LINK GLOSSARY} diameter and  30  @{"mils" LINK GLOSSARY}  hole.   Program  is  intensively
developed, and I'm going to make it a good  alternative  to  well  known  PC
software.

@ENDNODE
