                              @{b}@{fg shine}Reference section@{ub}@{fg text}

Here  is  a  detailed  description  of PCBDesigner toolbar,  menus, keys and
gadgets.

  @{" Toolbar   " LINK TOOLBAR}
  @{" Menus     " LINK MENUS}
  @{" Keyboard  " LINK KEYBOARD}
